
Step-by-step instructions to install Sass globally:

1. Open your terminal or command prompt.

2. Navigate to your project folder:
   cd "c:\Users\Lenovo\Desktop\Alx-Software-Eng\Prodev Frontend\Week2-two\semantic-html\alx-intermediate-frontend\0x03-sass_scss"

3. Install Sass globally using npm:
   npm install -g sass

4. Verify the installation by checking the Sass version:
   sass --version